column6: 2.51=Beginning in 2007,work=Opera several experimental builds have been released with Ogg Theora support. Full support for the video element is included in Presto 2.5.archiveurl= January 20101=Presto added very limited support for the ECMAScript API related to the audio element in version 2.0 using only the WAV PCM codec, while not implementing the element itself.url-status=dead  Full support for the audio element with the Ogg Vorbis and WAV codecs is included in Presto 2.5.
